CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 6, 1956, pg. 11, reads: "Celebrating - Marsha Portis, 1064 Rivermont Dr., celebrated her birthday with a gala party at her home.  Marsha, center, attends Gladstone Junior High School.  She is a junior Courier reporter and the daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Alexander Portis. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Marsha Portis dancing with young man, surrounded by other young women and men, during her birthday party in Portis home, 1064 Rivermont Drive, Glen Hazel
